{"tid":1145010,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港有無過一間咁既醫院？","createTime":"2019-05-08T11:55:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T12:52:42.000Z","uid":60321,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6e3f44da4cc9b5c4ab98bbb0fa2b196ff22ddadc","tid":1145010,"uid":60321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T11:55:34.000Z","msg":"幾年前發夢去左一間未見過既醫院 好深刻 <br />\n現實未見過 但硬係覺得好熟好似去過 <br />\n時代唔似依家 有種幾十年前既感覺<br />\n<br />\n個樣大約係藍藍 灰灰 黑黑既顏色<br />\n外型有啲粗線條 白色尖形窗 不斷重複既pattern<br />\n類似咁 但細隻啲<br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcR13cn7s2ixb0gARGRyOFFDfHqCbJ9gcqp1RZQFuilf5M2P3gWj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcR13cn7s2ixb0gARGRyOFFDfHqCbJ9gcqp1RZQFuilf5M2P3gWj&h=04f4ea51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n醫院一座過 但係三面圍住 前面可以的士落客<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n盡左力淨係描述到咁多 最記得係好沉既灰藍色<br />\n其實都未必存在 志在試下問一問 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbc8efb7b26c8a5cef0656dc6ba98d0aa05e0515","tid":1145010,"uid":60321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T11:57:05.000Z","msg":"三面圍住 意思係類似咁既格局<br />\n<img src=\"http://ubeat.com.cuhk.edu.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/oddpplandbuilding2-678x381.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fubeat.com.cuhk.edu.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2Foddpplandbuilding2-678x381.jpg&h=e5abc975&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但佢中間打橫個排會闊好多"},{"pid":"d9d38ab10251b815562fa8de621c9895bbb6aa4a","tid":1145010,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T11:58:09.000Z","msg":"唔知點解諗起原振俠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9d9eac634fb108a41c29222b9f7bd726092472d","tid":1145010,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T12:00:44.000Z","msg":"睇咗Inception？"},{"pid":"06acd670b789727b5da86df49750057b0ed2c118","tid":1145010,"uid":60321,"like":0,